<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.1.6">
<l>vāṉai yāramu tamtanta vaḷḷalai</l>
<l>tēṉai nīḷvayal cēṟaiyil kaṇṭupō</l>
<l>yāṉai vāṭṭiya ruḷuma marartam</l>
<l>kōṉai, yāmkuṭan taicceṉṟu kāṇṭumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having gone and seen in Cēṟai, with vast fields, [that] nectar,</l>
<l>The liberal [lord] who bestowed ambrosia that filled the heavens,</l>
<l>We will go and see in Kuṭantai the king of immortals</l>
<l>Who granted grace, destroying an elephant.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
